The paper proposes a novel approach to learning with graph-structured data in the problem domain of graph classification. This falls under the broad category of machine learning (cs.LG) and specifically deals with graph data, which could be categorized under computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), data structures (cs.DS), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
